## Configuration Explained

### OpenRouter Provider

**Available Models:**
- `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4` - Most capable Claude model
- `anthropic/claude-3.5-sonnet` - Fast and capable
- `google/gemini-2.5-pro-preview` - Best for long context (2M tokens)
- `google/gemini-2.5-flash-preview` - Fast and cheap
- `openai/gpt-4o` - OpenAI's latest multimodal model
- `openai/gpt-4o-mini` - Cheaper GPT-4 variant
- `openai/o1-preview` - Advanced reasoning model
- `deepseek/deepseek-chat` - Excellent coding model (cheap)
- `deepseek/deepseek-reasoner` - Deep reasoning capabilities
- `meta-llama/llama-3.3-70b-instruct` - Open source powerhouse
- `qwen/qwen-2.5-coder-32b-instruct` - Specialized coding model

**Why OpenRouter?**
- Access 100+ models with one API key
- Unified billing across all providers
- Automatic fallback if a model is down
- Pay only for what you use

### Perplexity Provider

**Available Models:**
- `sonar-pro` - Enhanced search with citations (default for web search)
- `sonar` - Fast search-augmented responses
- `sonar-reasoning` - Deep reasoning with web search

**Why Perplexity?**
- Real-time web search built-in
- Provides citations and sources
- Up-to-date information
- Great for research tasks

### Routing Strategy

```json
{
  "default": "openrouter,anthropic/claude-sonnet-4",
  "background": "openrouter,google/gemini-2.5-flash-preview",
  "think": "openrouter,openai/o1-preview",
  "longContext": "openrouter,google/gemini-2.5-pro-preview",
  "webSearch": "perplexity,sonar-pro"
}
```

**Explanation:**
- **Default**: Claude Sonnet 4 for general tasks (most capable)
- **Background**: Gemini Flash for simple operations (fast & cheap)
- **Think**: O1 Preview for complex reasoning (Plan mode)
- **Long Context**: Gemini Pro for huge contexts (2M token window)
- **Web Search**: Perplexity Sonar Pro for current information

