## Customization Options

### Budget-Conscious Configuration

Replace the Router section with:

```json
{
  "Router": {
    "default": "openrouter,deepseek/deepseek-chat",
    "background": "openrouter,google/gemini-2.5-flash-preview",
    "think": "openrouter,deepseek/deepseek-reasoner",
    "longContext": "openrouter,google/gemini-2.5-pro-preview",
    "webSearch": "perplexity,sonar"
  }
}
```

**Cost savings**: ~90% compared to using Claude Sonnet 4 for everything

