## Dynamic Model Switching

While using Claude Code, you can switch models on-the-fly:

### Switch to Different Models

```bash
# Use Claude Sonnet 4
/model openrouter,anthropic/claude-sonnet-4

# Use DeepSeek (cheap & good)
/model openrouter,deepseek/deepseek-chat

# Use O1 for reasoning
/model openrouter,openai/o1-preview

# Use Perplexity for web search
/model perplexity,sonar-pro

# Use Gemini Pro for long context
/model openrouter,google/gemini-2.5-pro-preview
```

### Common Scenarios

**Working on a complex algorithm:**
```
/model openrouter,openai/o1-preview
```

**Need current information:**
```
/model perplexity,sonar-pro
```

**Processing a huge codebase:**
```
/model openrouter,google/gemini-2.5-pro-preview
```

**Want to save money on simple tasks:**
```
/model openrouter,deepseek/deepseek-chat
```

