## Troubleshooting

### Error: "Invalid API Key"

**OpenRouter:**
```bash
# Check your key
echo $OPENROUTER_API_KEY

# Get a new key from https://openrouter.ai/keys
export OPENROUTER_API_KEY="sk-or-v1-..."

# Restart router
ccr restart
```

**Perplexity:**
```bash
# Check your key
echo $PERPLEXITY_API_KEY

# Get a new key from https://www.perplexity.ai/settings/api
export PERPLEXITY_API_KEY="pplx-..."

# Restart router
ccr restart
```

### Error: "Insufficient Credits"

**OpenRouter:**
- Visit https://openrouter.ai/account
- Add credits to your account

**Perplexity:**
- Visit https://www.perplexity.ai/settings/api
- Purchase API credits

### Router Won't Start

```bash
# Stop existing router
ccr stop

# Check logs
tail -f ~/.claude-code-router/logs/ccr-*.log

# Start with fresh config
ccr code
```

### Configuration Not Loading

```bash
# Check config file location
ls -la ~/.claude-code-router/config.json

# Validate JSON syntax
cat ~/.claude-code-router/config.json | python -m json.tool

# Use UI to fix issues
ccr ui
```

